<text top="55" left="90" width="103" height="14" font="1">Security Council</text>
<text top="55" left="732" width="96" height="14" font="1">3423rd meeting</text>
<text top="73" left="90" width="99" height="14" font="1">Forty-ninth year</text>
<text top="73" left="716" width="112" height="14" font="1">9 September 1994</text>
<text top="109" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">The Security Council has thus concluded the present</text>
<text top="127" left="90" width="321" height="14" font="1">stage of its consideration of the item on the agenda.</text>
<text top="109" left="512" width="316" height="14" font="1">The Security Council will remain seized of the</text>
<text top="127" left="481" width="42" height="14" font="1">matter.</text>
<text top="164" left="512" width="185" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 1.25 p.m.</i></text>
<text top="1084" left="821" width="8" height="14" font="1">3</text>
</page>
